"rameau antérieur du nerf cutané antebrachial médial ":" l.m. ramus anterior nervi cutanei antebrachii medialis   (TA) anterior branch of medial cutaneous nerve of forearme, anterior branch of medial antebrachial cutaneous nerve → nerf cutané médial de l’avant-bras ",
