"rameaux postérieurs des nerfs cervicaux ":" l.m.p. rami posteriores nervorum cervicalium, rami dorsales nervorum cervicalium   (TA) posterior rami of cervical nerves, dorsal rami of cervical nerves → nerfs cervicaux ",
"rameaux postérieurs des nerfs lombaires ":" l.m.p. rami posteriores nervorum lumbalium, rami dorsales nervorum lumbalium   (TA) posterior rami of lumbar nerves, dorsal rami of lumbar nerves → nerfs lombaires ",
"rameaux postérieurs des nerfs sacrés et coccygien ":" l.m.p. rami posteriores nervorum sacralium et nervi coccygei, rami dorsales nervorum sacralium et nervi coccygei   (TA) posterior rami of sacral nerves and coccygeal nerve, dorsal rami of sacral nerves and coccygeal nerve → nerfs sacrés et nerf coccygien ",
